{"tid":1282212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"追究到底？奉陪！我地比人嚇大架屌你老母 白色恐怖好撚驚呀","createTime":"2019-07-03T13:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:53:36.000Z","uid":133340,"like":361,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"40c583f41ce0634928f6b0c5fac5781ddf301fc4","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"警方證實，針對近日網上「起底」披露警員私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，以及攻擊警察網站等行為，網絡安全及科技罪案調查科昨日採取行動，指他們涉嫌不誠實使用電腦罪、未經同意披露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、刑事毀壞，以及威嚇作刑事毀壞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚驚呀黑警屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你大我呀</span></span></strong><br />\n我地唔係毅進仔、黑社會，唔係靠嚇就得既<br />\n重溫下歷史先　原來幾年前已經係咁恐嚇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好不安<br />\n睇下法庭會點判決先<br />\n<br />\n<ins>告唔入喎</ins><br />\n前年佔領運動期間，市場項目經理郭姓男子被指1分鐘內攻擊警務處網站1450次。他早前否認一項刑事損壞及一項有犯罪意圖而取用電腦的交替控罪，於屯門裁判法院受審，今午裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n裁判官水佳麗<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">質疑兩名警員的證供矛盾，指警員拘捕被告後沒有及時告知他聘請律師等法律權利，加上被告在睡夢中被弄醒，其精神狀態未必適合接受查問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>，認為警方做法對他構成不公，<span style=\"color: red;\">故裁定被告並非自願招供</strong></span>，拒絕將載有被告招認供辭的警員記事簿呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>另一單 撤控</ins><br />\n政府資訊科技總監辦公室於去年10月4日雨傘運動期間，發現警務處的網站受同一部電腦攻擊逾7,000次，警方循電腦的IP地址拘捕一名理大一年級學生。<strong>學生在警誡下承認與事件有關</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，惟警方再調查下發現，學生的電腦系統與攻擊警務處網站的電腦系統並不相同，發出攻擊的時間亦有異 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，獲撤銷控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>再另一單 上訴得直，撤銷定罪</ins><br />\n一名女市場推廣員被指在佔領運動期間，向警務處網站發動7,400次DDoS攻擊，早前被裁定刑事損壞罪成，被判80小時社會服務令。但她不服上訴，高等法院今日裁定她上訴得直，獲撤銷定罪。<br />\n「本席認為警方選擇<strong>在清晨近6時向被告人進行調查問話的確不是太理想的決定</strong>。但調查人員<span style=\"color: red;\">有問過被告人有否需要律師在場陪同正進行會面，被告人表示&ldquo;唔使&rdquo;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。調查人員<span style=\"color: red;\">亦有問過被告人的精神狀態才進行會面，當時被告人回答&ldquo;可以&rdquo;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。被告人在會面期間曾提及到在案發前幾天<strong>她出現頭痛，因此本席認為有需要看一看那錄影會面</strong>。本席看過整個錄影會面，期間特別留意被告人當時的精神狀態，實在見不到被告人在精神狀態上有倦態或有任何令人關注之處(太長，下刪)，最終上訴得直，撤銷定罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家全城玩白色恐怖亂咁塔左返去先講，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你地唔好亂講野亂認罪</span></strong><br />\n冇做過既野都比人嚇到話自己做左，我地都係奉公守法良好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>你係機械人，淨係識講名、地址、「我無野講」。</strong><br />\n睇電視都有教，認罪輕判永遠呃鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記清楚對方有冇講法律權利、自己有冇睡夢中被嘈醒<br />\n精神/身體狀態差呀頭痛呀頭暈呀之類，你知啦宜家啲後生掛住打機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後提醒大家一句，警察都話，有人涉嫌係網上犯法佢地會追究到底<br />\n宜家有人違法，唔係唔追究到底呀？<br />\n幾時死出黎回應呀屌你老母！<br />\n女警慫恿人衝入去煽動暴亂，係咪罪加一等架？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/80tjUx8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80tjUx8.jpg&h=b905b812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/9ghpmc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ghpmc8.jpg&h=40094a1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"034ff6339239b9008f2bf032accba337200ee68d","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"記清楚自己有咩法律權利，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對方有冇做足每一樣</span></strong><br />\n你知啦警察係執法架咋 法律對佢地黎講咁深<br />\n佢地唔識呀 唔記得呀 都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搜屋應對需知：<br />\n<br />\n（1）當警察要搜查處所，他們必須出示有效的搜查令，請務必檢查清楚搜查令是否有效：<br />\n- 必須有正確的被搜者名字（你的名字）<br />\n- 搜查令賦權搜查的地方（警只可搜該範圍）<br />\n- 懷疑已經或即將或意圖犯的罪行<br />\n- 搜查令下可檢取的物品<br />\n- 搜查令的有效期<br />\n- 裁判法院蓋印及裁判官簽署<br />\n（2）你有權要求有律師在場時先才開始進行搜查<br />\n（3）如需律師援助，請即聯絡請求協助<br />\n（4）你有權拍攝整個搜查過程<br />\n（5）未有列在搜查令入面的物品，你有權拒絕交給警察<br />\n（6）如果搜查令無包括搜查電腦電話內的資料，你可以拒絕解鎖<br />\n（7）搜查後可要求警察提供檢取物品列表副本"},{"pid":"7b03d469af3577a64b8795f6ececa93c05af1157","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9353b3698cde2ec253627354a5f450e4dda117ce","tid":1282212,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:53:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f47e15a0da307d9b71cf727f0c90708d58aa471","tid":1282212,"uid":258703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"227854bdeee3775ebdb00baa4ab8fc295c2d17b6","tid":1282212,"uid":11530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"14ddfa6da96cdb14a257b61ba87ff6b321021110","tid":1282212,"uid":55913,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"係啦 我中立既<br />\n阿sir應該兩邊都捉<br />\n無理由自己友就唔捉<br />\n<br />\n感覺好似好偏袒⋯"},{"pid":"11f3f07849d55e650c70d2b752ff370c6b12bbf6","tid":1282212,"uid":117468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 捉我呀<br />\n拉我呀"},{"pid":"bcac86c029878930ef70ee5e425ddb20bcc12b63","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:04:26.000Z","msg":"警犬驚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扮晒蟹咁強硬都係想玩白色恐怖<br />\n想人人自危<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/V0Zd3B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0Zd3B.gif&h=4459d871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n敵進我退，敵駐我擾， 敵疲我打，敵退我追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e64fe2bc3d81453ce1378171225d84a370731b","tid":1282212,"uid":112404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"拉我呀 黑警 屌你老母 快"},{"pid":"7ba827ae14a68b19ac07169f5df13dde4cd7ff70","tid":1282212,"uid":270946,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"推到差佬塔咗個知法犯法嘅女警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8535784de24037443dff3e602d18c38fa1498b7","tid":1282212,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"希望唔好再浪費納稅人既錢"},{"pid":"8b37b02a5b0be07ec8060650544c14fd8b3dc446","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"408298dfc1ce15a0355d44311df8046ff1836ae2","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcc3644082a1bf58fdf4a8f4965ddd6f8bd4413d","tid":1282212,"uid":241937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"推 各位頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b059cabaca99438ae41a11f48b2441ddf8fd77","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f31930695fd0d9edb5a98606fdb18543779d6a90","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1607a1ac97a43a2278da88a60532d91027ce2402","tid":1282212,"uid":133340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e4a2bc902e10d3068809a88e42f937040a99954","tid":1282212,"uid":36592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:44:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我無嘢講<br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我要見律師</span></span>"},{"pid":"4cc0505c3ac03c21b0f24603dd61ac